9.000Z","msg":"bookmarked<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"753bbc0141daa7cab6955392d3acd23c7b664a28","tid":611182,"uid":55732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"74348632d82dd0a021c1b53de902f9969fede3a7","tid":611182,"uid":136542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c2a2d55fd796058e6588db36e4441563550044de","tid":611182,"uid":55732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T02:16:40.000Z","msg":"聲優Radio<br />\n練聆聽一流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T03:15:37.000Z","msg":"話說聲優Radio有字幕？如果無字幕，我應該連查字典都做唔到......<br />\n<br />\n我連動畫有字幕的情況下，都唔係開處理得到一句完整句子。（要 replay 聽幾次）日劇字幕組會有啲會有中日對照就好啲。最後發覺既然要 reply N 次，都係電子小說最方便，又可以同時兼顧聆聽和閱讀。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T07:35:59.000Z","msg":"bilibili好似有啲有字幕版（我自己冇睇過，都係聽番嚟）<br />\n<br />\n但你個情況都係唔好咁快聽聲優Radio住<br />\n等到你再打好啲基礎先至試下<br />\n<br />\n因為聲優Radio練嘅係跟得上佢地日常對話嘅語速，即係你聽唔聽得切佢地講嘢<br />\n<br />\n動畫配音嘅語速其實算幾慢下，我諗大概N4至N3左右<br />\n新聞報道語速就N2<br />\n<br />\n而聲優Radio單人節目啲語速好多時快過聽新聞（我以NHK Radio嘅播音員做標準）<br />\n如果係幾個聲優一齊嗰啲節目個語速，再加埋啲笑聲雜音真係差唔多拍得住N1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b91d4387b7fc58c4ff640bdbaa6567c83b883b48","tid":611182,"uid":136542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"255ca82204ccdb7248502959f8f9cc32b8930635","tid":611182,"uid":77956,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T06:57:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www3.nhk.or.jp/news/easy/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww3.nhk.or.jp%2Fnews%2Feasy%2F&d=1rRYkwox2c35Iw131GJFok%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=e8a228f2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www3.nhk.or.jp/news/easy/</a><br />\n呢D你處唔處理到?<br />\n老實講睇動漫學唔係唔得,但你既vocab/語調可能會向奇怪既方向進發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n日劇會好少少既"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T08:37:54.000Z","msg":"呢個處理到，外來語加上漢字都可以唔洗查字典就估到個意思，平均一篇最多查一兩個字就可以睇晒。"},{"pid":"7bd5ef483ba0e8d02cfb95376aa0280d82ce1752","tid":611182,"uid":22018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T08:57:00.000Z","msg":"n4就正正經經買書學啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n學到n2左右再玩galgame/聽radio"}]}